ActNational Capital Act
Financial Administration Act
SubjectNational Capital Commission and the City of Ottawa ** Land exchange **
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to conclude a land exchange with the City of Ottawa in order to dispose of approximately 4,289.7 square metres of lands in favour of the City of Ottawa and to acquire approximately 4,249.2 square metres of lands from the City of Ottawa.
